product.name: Acrylic Hand Towel Box Cover Compatible with Kleenex Disposable Hand Towels Wall-Mounted Paper Towel Dispenser Suitable for Tabletop, Bathroom, Car, and Office Use (Glossy White)
product.description:
We believe that the family is everyone's safe haven, and the kitchen is a place to create beauty. We are committed to creating a harmonious and warm living environment for every family, and providing a spiritual habitat for every kitchen.
At TAINESS, We hope to create an ideal home space for our customers through this brand, so that they can enjoy the beauty of life in warmth and comfort, and together create a better home world.
We adhering to the concepts of high quality, careful design, practicality and convenience, we are committed to creating a comfortable, and unique home environment for you, so that you and your family can enjoy a happy time together and create wonderful memories.
We created this brand for several important reasons: to fulfill a market need, to provide unique value, and to create a better life.
product.bullet_points:
• 1.HAND TOWEL HOLDER: TAINESS disposable hand towels holder compatible with Kleenex Disposable Paper Hand Towels, not compatible with Kleenex hand towel in a pop-up box
• 2.WATERPROOF ACRYLIC MATERIAL: Our tissue hand towels box is made of high-quality sturdy acrylic material, which is waterproof, won't mold, easy to clean, beautiful and durable, ideal for use in the bathroom
• 3.WALL-MOUNTED: The paper towel box can be utilized by hanging it on the wall with the included hooks for convenient hand towel storage and saving the countertop space. Since we have to reserve space for wall hooks, the interior of the acrylic box will be a bit larger than the tissue box
• 4.BOTTOM MAGNETIC DESIGN: The bottom of the hand towel cover is designed as a push-pull magnetic switch, whether the box is hung on the wall or to put in the bathroom handle, this design can make the change of paper towel box becomes more convenient
• 5.WIDE RANGE OF APPLICATIONS: Suitable for sinks, bathrooms, kitchens, bedrooms, living rooms, patios, cars, offices and many other scenes
